        "text": "=🧪 *Clinical Trial Document Processed*\n\n*Study:* {{ $('Format Trial Data').item.json.studyId }}\n*Protocol:* {{ $('Format Trial Data').item.json.protocolNumber }}\n*Phase:* {{ $('Format Trial Data').item.json.phase }}\n*Sponsor:* {{ $('Format Trial Data').item.json.sponsor }}\n\n📋 *Study Overview:*\n• Indication: {{ $('Format Trial Data').item.json.indication }}\n• Design: {{ $('Format Trial Data').item.json.studyDesign }}\n• Duration: {{ $('Format Trial Data').item.json.studyDuration }}\n\n👥 *Sample Size:*\n• Target: {{ $('Format Trial Data').item.json.sampleTarget }}\n• Enrolled: {{ $('Format Trial Data').item.json.sampleEnrolled }}\n• Completed: {{ $('Format Trial Data').item.json.sampleCompleted }}\n\n🎯 *Primary Endpoint:*\n{{ $('Format Trial Data').item.json.primaryEndpoint }}\n\n📊 *Secondary Endpoints:* {{ $('Format Trial Data').item.json.secondaryCount }}\n\n⚠️ *Safety:*\n• Total AEs: {{ $('Format Trial Data').item.json.aeTotal }}\n• Serious AEs: {{ $('Format Trial Data').item.json.aeSAE }}\n• Common: {{ $('Format Trial Data').item.json.aeCommon }}\n\n🔗 <https://drive.google.com/file/d/{{ $('Format Trial Data').item.json.fileId }}/view|View Document>",
